VALUES
  ('medical-tech-moex-06698', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-108-0356504f', 'sub-medical-tech-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '近年來發現先天性淋巴細胞（innate lymphoid cell, ILC）分為三個亞群，其中ILC2在活化後，可釋放如IL-5 及IL-13的細胞激素，進⽽激活肥⼤細胞（mast cells）及嗜酸性球（eosinophils）等。下述何種細胞激素組 合可促使ILC2的⽣成及活化？', '["IL-7, IL-12, IL-15", "IL-7, TSLP, IL-33, IL-25", "IL-7, IL-4", "IL-7, IL-1, IL-23"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:16:28+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "5103d6329d85", "answer_pdf_sha1": "8b78dcca3f9b", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "108030", "c": "308", "s": "66", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床血清免疫學與臨床病毒學", "year": "108", "exam_name": "108年第一次專技人員高等考試醫師牙醫師藥師考試分階段考試、醫事檢驗師、醫事放射師、物理治療師、職能治療師、呼吸治療師、獸醫師考試", "original_question_number": 39, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-06699', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-108-0356504f', 'sub-medical-tech-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '活化的T細胞（activated T cells）或調控型T細胞（Regulatory T cells, Treg）上常有CD25的表現。CD25是 什麼分⼦？', '["the α chain of the IL-2 receptor", "the βchain of the IL-2 receptor", "common βchain", "common γchain"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:16:28+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "5103d6329d85", "answer_pdf_sha1": "8b78dcca3f9b", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "108030", "c": "308", "s": "66", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床血清免疫學與臨床病毒學", "year": "108", "exam_name": "108年第一次專技人員高等考試醫師牙醫師藥師考試分階段考試、醫事檢驗師、醫事放射師、物理治療師、職能治療師、呼吸治療師、獸醫師考試", "original_question_number": 40, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
